  "text": "A significant correlation between the location of placing smokeless tobacco and the location of oral lesions were identified in this study (p= 0.0001) which is also in agreement with the findings of Kaugars et al. [CITATION_1] , Wray and Guirt [CITATION_2] and Ayo-Yusuf et al. [CITATION_3] .",
